{"atom_id": "ig34_p0284_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 284, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Relating the datasets (as described in Section 8, Representing Relationships and Data) is the simplest method; however, all time-point concentrations in PC must be used to calculate all parameters for all subjects.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": ["\u00a78"], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0284_a011", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 284, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If datasets cannot be related, then individual subject records must be related.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0284_a012", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 284, "page_region": "bottom", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "In either case, the values of PCGRPID and PPGRPID must take into account multiple analytes and multiple reference time points, if they exist.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "HEADING", "verbatim": "PC-PP \u2013 Suggestions for Implementing RELREC in the Submission of PK Data", "heading_level": 6, "sibling_index": 8, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Determine which of the scenarios best reflects how PP data are related to PC data.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Questions that should be considered include:", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "Do all parameters for each PK profile use all concentrations for all subjects?", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "LIST_ITEM", "verbatim": "If so, create a PPGRPID value for all PP records and a PCGRPID value for all PC records for each profile for each subject, analyte, and reference time point.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Decide whether to relate datasets or records.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "If choosing the latter, create records in RELREC for each PCGRPID value and each PPGRPID value (method A).", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Use RELID to show which PCGRPID and PPGRPID records are related.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0285_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 285, "page_region": "middle", "parent_section": "\u00a76.3.5.9.3 Relating PP Records to PC Records", "atom_type": "SENTENCE", "verbatim": "Consider RELREC methods B, C, and D as applicable.", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:writer", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.3", "ts": "2026-04-27T01:49:12.330710Z"}}
